videos.description: Facing Syracuse's 2-3 zone, Clemson decides to go over the top with Gabe DeVoe throwing the perfect lob to Jaron Blossomgame for the monster, alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Clemson finds alley-oops are the way to beat the zone
